}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== FCC label in the submission shows the device is a (presumably Askey) WLL6160-D4.
'''[[Toshiba]]''' P/N: PA3722U-1MPC (some Toshiba modules with this P/N may instead be other AR5B95 modules, such as the [[Lite-On WN6601A]]). :Additional ''model'' of G86C0004A410
"3017-009090" is silkscreened on the top of the board of some units. "08B1-0VX0100" may be silkscreened on the board of other units (different Askey model #?).
FCC photos show a label on the device with an OUI of 00:1B:9E. FCC photos also show a full-size version of the card - an '''Askey''' WLL6170-D4.
